OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FA man who was abused by his partner
OL,7,Fsays he's 'disappointed' after she
OL,8,Freceived a suspended sentence.
OL,10,FSarah Rigby, 41, had pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour
OL,12,Fover her former partner Gareth Jones.
OL,14,FRigby, from Winsford in Cheshire, was
OL,15,Fsentenced to 20 months in prison,
OL,16,Fsuspended, on Friday 24 May. She was
OL,17,Falso handed a five year restraining
OL,18,Forder and ordered to complete 35 days
OL,19,Fof rehabilitation.
