OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Granada Reports after
OL,7,Fher sentencing, Mr Jones voiced his
OL,8,Ffrustration after she avoided jail
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FHe said: "I feel disappointed with the
OL,12,Fverdict, it shows there is still a
OL,13,Fstigma in society about the male-
OL,14,Ffemale dynamic, especially relating to
OL,15,Fdomestic abuse. If it was a man it
OL,16,Fwould probably be a completely
OL,17,Fdifferent outcome.
