OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,F"Females can be perpetrators, public
OL,7,Fopinion is vital, and changing the
OL,8,Fnarrative is key and that
OL,9,Fstigmatisation is out there in society
OL,10,Faround how males are not seen as
OL,11,Fvictims of domestic violence. It shows
OL,12,Fthis can happen and more people do
OL,13,Fneed to come forward and speak out
OL,14,Fabout this."
OL,16,FThe relationship began in July 2021,
OL,17,Fand quickly turned into what police
OL,18,Flater described as one of the worst
OL,19,Fcases of controlling and coercive
OL,20,Fbehaviour they'd ever encountered.
