OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,F"Over the time I was with Sarah I was
OL,7,Fsubjected to psychological abuse, not
OL,8,Fbeing given a key to the property, and
OL,9,Fbeing forced to leave on numerous
OL,10,Foccasions.
OL,12,F"I was belittled, called names each
OL,13,Ftime, the constant bombardment of text
OL,14,Fmessages, the mental health aspect,
OL,15,Fthe physical impact, financial control
OL,16,Fand taking all of my salary and not
OL,17,Fbeing able to use the bathroom in the
OL,18,Fhouse."
