OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FAfter nine months with Rigby, Gareth
OL,7,Fcontacted police in March 2022, after
OL,8,Fseeking help from a men's domestic
OL,9,Fabuse helpline.
OL,11,FFollowing the call, an investigation
OL,12,Fwas launched by detectives in
OL,13,FNorthwich CID and Rigby was later
OL,14,Fcharged.
OL,16,FIn that time, she had forced him to
OL,17,Fmove into her home in Winsford, where
OL,18,Fhe was made to store all his
OL,19,Fbelongings in the garage.
