OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FShe ordered him to pay #700 a month
OL,7,Frent, despite the fact her father
OL,8,Falready owned the house.
OL,10,FRigby soon took full control of all
OL,11,Fhis finances, cut him off from his
OL,12,Ffamily and friends, and stopped him
OL,13,Ffrom being in the house alone `
OL,14,Fdespite the fact he needed to work
OL,15,Ffrom home. He would be forced to go to
OL,16,Fthe local library to keep working.
