OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FGareth was also told he was unable to
OL,7,Fshower or defecate at the house,
OL,8,Fmeaning that he had to go to a local
OL,9,Fgym to wash. She also searched him as
OL,10,Fhe was entering and leaving the house
OL,11,Fto ensure he wasn't taking anything
OL,12,Fthat she didn't approve of.
OL,14,FIf he didn't comply with her orders,
OL,15,FRigby would punish him by physically
OL,16,Fassaulting him, preventing him from
OL,17,Feating, and making the victim sleep on
OL,18,Fthe floor with no duvet and the
OL,19,Fwindows left open.
