OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,FDuring the relationship, Gareth lost
OL,7,Ffour stone in weight.
OL,9,FHe told ITV Granada Reports: "I became
OL,10,Fmore and more systematically thrown
OL,11,Fout of the house. My mum had offered
OL,12,Fto cook some food but I became so
OL,13,Fnervous about eating anything that had
OL,14,Fonion or garlic in that I wouldn't eat.
OL,16,F"I became very nervous and asked
OL,17,Fconstantly what's in the food, for
OL,18,Ffear of retribution."
OL,20,FThat retribution often came.
