OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,F"Rigby had a stranglehold on the
OL,7,Fvictim. Through her coercive behaviour
OL,8,Fshe was able to control everything he
OL,9,Fdid, cutting him off from everyone he
OL,10,Fknew and leaving him trapped, feeling
OL,11,Flike he had nowhere to turn.
OL,13,F"Her actions left the victim both
OL,14,Fphysically and emotionally scarred,
OL,15,Fand even now, two years after their
OL,16,Frelationship ended, he is still
OL,17,Freceiving phycological counselling to
OL,18,Fhelp him recover.
