OL,3,CMan opens up on nine months of abuse
OL,4,Cafter partner handed suspended sentence
OL,6,F"Even after she was charged, Rigby
OL,7,Fcontinued to taunt her victim,
OL,8,Frefusing to return his belongings, and
OL,9,Fconstantly delaying the trial by
OL,10,Ffailing to notify the court of
OL,11,Fholidays and appointments.
OL,13,F"Although she eventually pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to her offending, she has shown
OL,15,Fno remorse for her actions. While the
OL,16,Fvictim will never be able to forget
OL,17,Fwhat happened to him, I hope that the
OL,18,Fconclusion of this case will help him
OL,19,Fto move forward and start to rebuild
OL,20,Fhis life."
