OL,6,FGareth now hopes his case can act as a
OL,7,Fcatalyst to change the way people
OL,8,Fthink about domestic abuse, when men
OL,9,Fare the victims.
OL,11,F"Hopefully, we can change the way the
OL,12,Fjudicial system looks upon these kinds
OL,13,Fof cases as has shown with the verdict
OL,14,Fthat has come out. I think that's
OL,15,Fvitally important on how we can try
OL,16,Fand move things forward as a society.
